   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Help us Train 1,000 Teachers in Dadaab</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will train 1,000 Refugee Teachers in the World&apos;s Largest Refugee Camp, at Dadaab, in Kenya. Home to over 300,000 refugees, Dadaab is one of the world&apos;s largest refugee camps. Almost one half of it&apos;s population is made up of school-aged children in desperate need of an education and quality teachers. Unfortunately, UNHCR says that 80% of the teachers in the camp are untrained refugees. We aim to target these passionate teachers and give them the training they need to succeed.</narrative>
  </description>
